CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FDrivers sat idly in Birmingham traffic
OL,8,Fhas risen by 6% despite the efforts of
OL,9,Fthe Clean Air Zone (CAZ) to get cars
OL,10,Foff the roads.
OL,12,FThe clean air zone was introduced in
OL,13,F2021 as a way to try to crack down on
OL,14,Fair pollution.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council defined it as,
OL,8,F"An area where targeted action is
OL,9,Ftaken to improve air quality, in
OL,10,Fparticular by discouraging the most
OL,11,Fpolluting vehicles from entering the
OL,12,Fzone. No vehicle is banned in the
OL,13,Fzone, but those which do not have
OL,14,Fclean enough engines will have to pay
OL,15,Fa daily charge if they travel within
OL,16,Fthe area."
OL,18,FBreathing in polluted air affects our
OL,19,Fhealth and costs the NHS and our
OL,20,Fsociety billions of pounds each year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FAir pollution is recognised as a
OL,8,Fcontributing factor in the onset of
OL,9,Fheart disease and cancer, and can
OL,10,Fcause a range of health impacts,
OL,11,Fincluding effects on lung function,
OL,12,Fexacerbation of asthma, increases in
OL,13,Fhospital admissions and mortality.
OL,15,FThe main air quality issue in
OL,16,FBirmingham is elevated levels of
OL,17,Fnitrogen dioxide (NO2), particularly
OL,18,Fwithin the City Centre area as a
OL,19,Fresult of road traffic emissions.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FMonitoring results generally show that
OL,8,Fconcentrations have been declining
OL,9,Fover the last 5 years, although
OL,10,Fexceedances persist at a few
OL,11,Flocations. A city-wide air Quality
OL,12,FManagement Area (AQMA) was declared in
OL,13,F2003.
OL,15,FThe council says that whilst air
OL,16,Fquality has improved significantly in
OL,17,Frecent decades, there are some areas
OL,18,Fwhere local action is needed to
OL,19,Fprotect people and the environment
OL,20,Ffrom the effects of air pollution.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FBirmingham City Council adopted an Air
OL,8,FQuality Action Plan in 2021, which set
OL,9,Fout 7 broad actions that are being
OL,10,Fundertaken to improve air quality.
OL,11,FHowever, the singular driving project
OL,12,Flikely to deliver measurably improved
OL,13,Fair quality and be most visible to
OL,14,Fcitizens is the Clean Air Zone (CAZ),
OL,15,Fwhich became operational in June 2021.
OL,17,FIn the CAZ area, NO2 concentrations
OL,18,Fshown further reductions, and vehicle
OL,19,Fcompliance rates have continued to
OL,20,Fimprove, albeit at a slower rate.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FWe will continue to monitor and
OL,8,Fevaluate the impact of the CAZ on air
OL,9,Fquality. The council said it will
OL,10,Fdevelop a new AQAP for adoption in
OL,11,F2026.
OL,13,FEfforts to reduce traffic in the city
OL,14,Fcentre have been made through the City
OL,15,FCentre Movement and Access Strategy
OL,16,F(rationalisation and restriction of
OL,17,Ftraffic movements), and work continues
OL,18,Fto improve public transport
OL,19,Finfrastructure.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FThe work includes developing the
OL,8,FSprint and cross-city bus networks,
OL,9,Fexpanding the Midland Metro network,
OL,10,Fand reopening the Camp Hill railway
OL,11,Fline to provide new stations at
OL,12,FMoseley Village, Kings Heath, and
OL,13,FPineapple Road, which are now due to
OL,14,Fbecome operational by the end of 2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FBut there are still traffic hotspots
OL,8,Fin the city. According to the traffic
OL,9,Fmonitoring service Inrix, people who
OL,10,Fregularly travel on the Pershore Road
OL,11,Fat 4 pm spend an extra 40 hours in
OL,12,Ftraffic compared to someone commuting
OL,13,Fat off-peak times.
OL,15,FThat means getting regularly caught at
OL,16,Frush hour between Belgrave Middleway
OL,17,Fand Watford Road can mean you spend
OL,18,Falmost 2 extra days a year sitting in
OL,19,Ftraffic.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FThe latest figures for air pollution
OL,8,Fonly go up to the end of 2024, with
OL,9,Flast year's data set to be published
OL,10,Fin June of this year, between July and
OL,11,FSeptember.
OL,13,FThe 2024 data showed that the average
OL,14,Flevel of nitrogen dioxide within the
OL,15,Fzone was down 22.5% from 2019 (pre-
OL,16,Fpandemic levels).
OL,18,FMeanwhile, almost 150 (149.9) million
OL,19,Fpounds had been raised by the clean
OL,20,Fair zone by the end of last March.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772062278
OL,3,CDrivers idle in Birmingham traffic
OL,4,Crises despite efforts to drop car
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FThe number of non-compliant vehicles
OL,8,Fentering the zone has reduced from
OL,9,Faround 15% when the scheme began to
OL,10,Fjust 3.4% last month.
OL,12,FBut the average number of different
OL,13,Fvehicles detected in the zone every
OL,14,Fsingle day increased from 88,609 in
OL,15,FJanuary 2022 to 97,481 in January this
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
